    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "These sets of rockets come in pairs and strap onto existing footwear (or a creature's feet). Inserting them and aligning them properly takes 1 minute. When you Activate the blast boots, you can High Jump or Long Jump, without the need to Stride first. Higher-level versions increase the distance of your High Jump or Long Jump.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 159,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
